  Attack window: 2026-05-11 around 19:20-19:30 UTC.
  Impact: malicious npm lifecycle payloads can exfiltrate developer, cloud, GitHub,
  npm, Kubernetes, Vault, SSH, AI-tool, and wallet credentials; some reports also
  describe persistence and destructive token-monitor behaviour.

  Immediate check:

    aidevops security supply-chain scan          # scan repos.json + ~/Git repos
